short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Use wormworld skins in any other extension. And free the rooms.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: WormWorld has been attacked in several ways during its 3 years of existence. And many things that our team developed were copied and distributed without permission and without even saying Thanks. So let's work on top of all the extensions so that everyone can use all the resources.
